    <p>You can include the font and font software in software-only apps.</p>
    <p>You must not use the font software in apps or equipment that you sell.</p>
    <p>If you want to use Frutiger Light in an app, you must buy your own licence. The sub-licence does not cover this.</p>
  </div>
</details>

<details class="nhsuk-details">
  <summary class="nhsuk-details__summary">
    <span class="nhsuk-details__summary-text">
